<h1>Samina's Corner Store</h1>

<div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 40px auto;">
    <!-- Project Overview Section -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
        <h2 style="font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">About</h2>
        <p style="color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            Samina's Corner Store is a small, family-run business that processes approximately 50 daily transactions 
            from its ~100 regular customers and maintains inventory for roughly 20 unique products.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.7;">
            Currently, sales and inventory are tracked using an outdated, error-prone paper log, resulting in frequent 
            stockouts of popular items and an estimated 10% loss in sales annually due to poor data management. 
            This database-driven website solves these issues by integrating customer, product, supplier, and order data 
            into a single system, enabling accurate inventory tracking, customer purchase history, and automated sales reporting.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
        <h2 style="font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">Getting Started</h2>
        <p style="color: #4a5568;">
            Use the navigation menu above to manage:
        </p>
        <ul style="color: #4a5568; margin-top: 12px; padding-left: 20px;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 6px;"><strong>Browse</strong> - View all customers, orders, products, and inventory</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 6px;"><strong>Add</strong> - Create new records in any table</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 6px;"><strong>Delete</strong> - Remove existing records</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 6px;"><strong>Tools</strong> - Test delete functionality and reset database</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

